{"tid":876820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"耶穌算唔算係好人","createTime":"2018-10-26T01:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T03:44:36.000Z","uid":187905,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55045d6d6dbb21f35ecb45cd313aecafaab047e7","tid":876820,"uid":187905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"講緊如果真係有耶穌呢個人<br />\n如果耶穌做同講d野係真咁佢一定係好人<br />\n我個人覺得耶穌做d神蹟係假，即係佢係一個好勁嘅魔術師，早過晒現代人學識玩魔術，咩五餅二魚，水變酒，復活都只係魔術，靠工具/掩眼法做出嚟，所謂12門徒其實係助手嚟<br />\n用魔術等人信服佢，佢d演講都都叫導人向善，仲強化左天主教同基督教個根基，不過都肯定有d私心想人當佢神咁拜先咁做<br />\n利申 唔信"},{"pid":"5aee0391543566b86d9aed2c923371c324a2c695","tid":876820,"uid":90820,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:48:28.000Z","msg":"多得耶穌跣猶大<br />\n我今日先有得戴住個十字架喺學校教聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555162e9866d128d7c2c5434fca70f6b37c04789","tid":876820,"uid":214016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"耶穌係神黎架，跌左落凡間咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fbba94b32b0b7b5913a814c1584c3cb4925e4e","tid":876820,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"耶穌操到咁大隻都可以俾人捉到<br />\n釘係十字架"},{"pid":"3191621317ed91d8c65cc9926c337716374bb16b","tid":876820,"uid":187905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aee0391543566b86d9aed2c923371c324a2c695","tid":876820,"uid":90820,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:48:28.000Z","msg":"多得耶穌跣猶大<br />\n我今日先有得戴住個十字架喺學校教聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:01:08.000Z","msg":"可能己經夾好左埸戲，唔係耶穌點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fed642f1288ddc1513fb334c5f2adace096d2a8","tid":876820,"uid":90820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3191621317ed91d8c65cc